MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: Mapping to load sales data to Gross margin table
MAPPING.NAME: m_B2B_GRSMRGNLOAD_SALS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Join Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: ORD_NBR1 = ORD_NBR AND CONF_NBR1 = CONF_NBR AND TYPE1 = TYPE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT Reference.Desc_1 as Desc_1, Reference.Desc_2 as Desc_2, 1 as DUMMY FROM DBO.Reference Reference with (NOLOCK) WHERE REFERENCE_KEY ='DTC_ONEWORLD_Mapping' and reference_sub_key_1='Sold_to'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_ID as FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_NAME as FACILITY_NAME FROM SLBA_FACILITY SLBA_FACILITY

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Used to get the day_dimension lookup values
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_DAY_DIMENSION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE as AS_OF_DATE, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_MONTH_NUM as CY_MONTH_NUM, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY as CY_YEAR_YYYY, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_WK_OF_YEAR as CY_WK_OF_YEAR, DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE as DAY_DATE FROM DAY_DIMENSION DAY_DIMENSION

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Rows are fetched from source qualifier
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_DTC2_SLSLN

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DTC2_SLSLN.ORD_NBR, DTC2_SLSLN.SEQ_NBR, DTC2_SLSLN.TYPE, DTC2_SLSLN.CONF_NBR, DTC2_SLSLN.BTB_BTC_SW, DTC2_SLSLN.STYLE, DTC2_SLSLN.SIZE_CD, DTC2_SLSLN.COLOR, DTC2_SLSLN.LINE_SHP_VIA, DTC2_SLSLN.RTN_REASON_CD, DTC2_SLSLN.ITEM_QTY_ORDERED, DTC2_SLSLN.PKG_QTY_ORDERED, DTC2_SLSLN.LINE_TAX_AMT, DTC2_SLSLN.LINE_SHPCHG_AMT, DTC2_SLSLN.LINE_TOT_AMT, DTC2_SLSLN.LINE_FREIGHT_TAX_AMT FROM DTC2_SLSLN DTC2_SLSLN WHERE DTC2_SLSLN.PROCESS_FLAG IS NULL AND DTC2_SLSLN.TYPE in ('REGULAR','REPLACE')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CDE = I_STYLE_CDE AND SIZE_CDE = I_SIZE_CDE AND COLOR = I_COLOR

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT b2b_cost_at_style.Unit_Cost as Unit_Cost, b2b_cost_at_style.Dim_Style_ID as Dim_Style_ID, b2b_cost_at_style.Begin_Date as Begin_Date, COALESCE(b2b_cost_at_style.End_Date,99991231) as End_Date FROM DTC.b2b_cost_at_style b2b_cost_at_style WITH (NOLOCK)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: Dim_Style_ID = I_Dim_Style_ID AND Begin_Date <= I_Begin_Date AND End_Date >= I_End_Date

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: LOOKUP TO GENERATE THE ITEM_PER_PK BASED ON ITEM_ID
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_DTC_ITEM_UNITS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRIM(DTC_ITEM.ITEM_ID) as ITEM_ID, DTC_ITEM.ITEMS_PER_PK as ITEMS_PER_PK FROM DTC_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DTC_ITEM.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, 1 as DUMMY FROM DTC_ITEM WHERE STYLE_CDE='DR-NS' --

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CDE = STYLE_CDE1 AND SIZE_CDE = SIZE_CDE1 AND COLOR = COLOR1

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Rows are fetched from source qualifier
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_DTC2_SLSHD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DTC2_SLSHD.ORD_NBR, DTC2_SLSHD.SEQ_NBR, DTC2_SLSHD.TYPE, DTC2_SLSHD.CLKNO, DTC2_SLSHD.DAY_DATE, DTC2_SLSHD.ORDER_TYPE_CD, DTC2_SLSHD.SRCE_CD, DTC2_SLSHD.CONF_NBR, DTC2_SLSHD.ORIG_CONF_NBR, NVL(DTC2_SLSHD.CUSTMST_ACCT_NBR,0), DTC2_SLSHD.ZIP, DTC2_SLSHD.PH_CODE, DTC2_SLSHD.ORDER_DT, DTC2_SLSHD.CORRECTED_DT, DTC2_SLSHD.PROCESS_DT, DTC2_SLSHD.EXPIRED_DT, DTC2_SLSHD.EVENT_ID, DTC2_SLSHD.BRAND, DTC2_SLSHD.EVT_CLASS, DTC2_SLSHD.DRPCD, DTC2_SLSHD.BTB_BTC_SW FROM DTC2_SLSHD DTC2_SLSHD WHERE DTC2_SLSHD.TYPE in ('REGULAR','REPLACE') AND DTC2_SLSHD.PROCESS_FLAG IS NULL

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT Dim_Item.Dim_Style_Id as Dim_Style_Id, Dim_Item.Item_id as Item_id FROM DBO.Dim_Item Dim_Item WITH (NOLOCK)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Expression to set values for lookup
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_LOOKUP_QTY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DTC_ITEM.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, DTC_ITEM.STYLE_CDE as STYLE_CDE, DTC_ITEM.SIZE_CDE as SIZE_CDE, DTC_ITEM.COLOR as COLOR FROM DTC_ITEM DTC_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CDE = STYLE AND SIZE_CDE = O_SIZE_CD AND COLOR = O_COLOR

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(IN(TYPE,'REGULAR','REPLACE') = 1 and SOURCE_ORDER_TYPE='00','OS COGS' ,'Other Std COGS Adjs')
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: COST_MEASURE_NAME

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT XRF_ACC.CUST_SEQ_NBR as CUST_SEQ_NBR, XRF_ACC.SOLDTO as SOLDTO FROM XRF_ACC WHERE ts_div_cde='DR'
